{
  "title": "支持 Markdown 语法吗？",
  "slug": 575717,
  "body_html": "<h2 id=\"ivfprb\" data-type=\"h\"><a class=\"anchor\" id=\"现有语法\" href=\"#ivfprb\"></a>现有语法</h2><div data-type=\"p\"></div><p data-type=\"p\">语雀目前支持基本的 Markdown 语法：</p><p data-type=\"p\"></p><ul data-type=\"unordered-list\"><li data-type=\"list-item\" data-list-type=\"unordered-list\"><p data-type=\"p\">标题</p></li><li data-type=\"list-item\" data-list-type=\"unordered-list\"><p data-type=\"p\">有序列表</p></li><li data-type=\"list-item\" data-list-type=\"unordered-list\"><p data-type=\"p\">无序列表</p></li><li data-type=\"list-item\" data-list-type=\"unordered-list\"><p data-type=\"p\">任务列表</p></li><li data-type=\"list-item\" data-list-type=\"unordered-list\"><p data-type=\"p\">代码</p></li><li data-type=\"list-item\" data-list-type=\"unordered-list\"><p data-type=\"p\">代码块</p></li><li data-type=\"list-item\" data-list-type=\"unordered-list\"><p data-type=\"p\">加粗</p></li><li data-type=\"list-item\" data-list-type=\"unordered-list\"><p data-type=\"p\">斜体</p></li><li data-type=\"list-item\" data-list-type=\"unordered-list\"><p data-type=\"p\">引入</p></li></ul><p data-type=\"p\"></p><div data-type=\"p\">具体使用方式，输入 Markdown 语法特殊标示，空格进入输入文本状态。下面是操作示例：</div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\"><div data-type=\"image\" data-display=\"block\" data-align=\"center\" data-src=\"https://lark-assets-prod.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/2018/gif/62bef532-ad3e-41f9-87ae-47d6c1eee71e.gif\" data-width=\"832\"><img src=\"https://lark-assets-prod.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/2018/gif/62bef532-ad3e-41f9-87ae-47d6c1eee71e.gif\" width=\"832\"/></div></div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\">更多详细 Markdown 语法说明，请查看 <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://yuque.com/yuque/help/dive-into-yuque-editor\" class=\"bi-link\">深入浅出可视化文档编辑器</a></div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><h2 id=\"so3ggk\" data-type=\"h\"><a class=\"anchor\" id=\"导入-markdown-文件\" href=\"#so3ggk\"></a>导入 Markdown 文件</h2><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\">通过编辑的「文档」-「导入」，选择你需要导入的 Markdown 文件，即可完成导入。</div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\"><div data-type=\"image\" data-display=\"block\" data-align=\"center\" data-src=\"https://lark-assets-prod.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/2018/png/14cf19b5-26b8-4cf6-adf7-d1328d5cd211.png\" data-width=\"350\"><img src=\"https://lark-assets-prod.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/2018/png/14cf19b5-26b8-4cf6-adf7-d1328d5cd211.png\" width=\"350\"/></div></div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\"></div>"
}